# Predefined Callback Structures

**API Collection**

CFBag provides some predefined callbacks for your convenience.

## Constants

- **kCFTypeBagCallBacks**
- **kCFCopyStringBagCallBacks**: Predefined [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFBagCallBacks] structure containing a set of callbacks appropriate for use when the values in a CFBag are all CFString objects. The bag makes immutable copies of the strings placed into it.
